OL,3,CChild hospitalised after South Shields
OL,4,Croad traffic incident
OL,6,FA chid has been taken to hospital
OL,7,Fafter a road traffic incident on South
OL,8,FTyneside.
OL,10,FParamedics confirmed they were called
OL,11,Fto South Promenade in South Shields at
OL,12,F3:19pm on Saturday (27 June).
OL,14,FAn adult was also taken to hospital
OL,15,Ffor further treatment.
