OL,3,CChild hospitalised after South Shields
OL,4,Croad traffic incident
OL,6,FA North East Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We received a call
OL,8,Fat 3.19pm on Saturday 27 June to
OL,9,Freports of a road traffic incident on
OL,10,FSouth Promenade in South Shields. We
OL,11,Fdispatched an ambulance crew, a
OL,12,Fspecialist paramedic, a rapid response
OL,13,Fparamedic, and a clinical team leader
OL,14,Fto the scene.
OL,16,F"Two patients were taken to hospital
OL,17,Ffor further treatment."
